import React from "react";

export const PorcoRossoAviaoSVG = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      width="356"
      height="282"
      viewBox="0 0 356 282"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
    >
      <ellipse cx="178" cy="141" rx="178" ry="141" fill="url(#pattern0)" />
      <defs>
        <pattern
          id="pattern0"
          patternContentUnits="objectBoundingBox"
          width="1"
          height="1"
        >
          <use
            xlinkHref="#image0_1_17"
            transform="matrix(0.00142727 0 0 0.0018018 -0.230762 0)"
          />
        </pattern>
        <image
          id="image0_1_17"
          width="1024"
          height="555"
        />
      </defs>
    </svg>
  );
};
